{"tid":835713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼高鐵、創科局後，金管局準備借「一帶一路」幫香港人送錢","createTime":"2018-09-25T06:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T11:10:18.000Z","uid":149494,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"acb4c96186606326e4a48831d66547a3fb1b7278","tid":835713,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:23:40.000Z","msg":"高鐵拎左香港人八百幾億, 結果客流量連當初估計一半都無, 而所謂便利香港人到大灣區發展又係得個鳩up，最大贏家又係負責起既國企<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n創科局洗左香港人幾百億, 唔洗問, 又係關你香港人撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本唔係為左培養香港科研人才, 最大贏家係大陸所謂科技公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黎緊金管局準備聯同大陸企業投資一帶一路, 又係明正言順搶香港人錢, 最大贏家又係大陸企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲未計豆腐渣沙中線工程超支d錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴線香港人有錢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好拋of自己係香港人囉真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d9273fe5975c640cd1931403dcb996965d8b1c","tid":835713,"uid":62842,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7c5258a4f82d3f7d4beea4ed682831bb2f16ec","tid":835713,"uid":161168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42416c768671c84b43bf4a7990dde7b82211a13","tid":835713,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6052c0c20f25d2cac60445476c85e688f5595c34","tid":835713,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"支那狗依家無錢叫雞啦，唔搵你搵邊個？<img src